HEADWORD: Guilder
<hw>Guil"der</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D.
<ets>gulden</ets>, orig., <ets>golden</ets>. Cf. <er>Golden</er>.]</ety>
